node.title: Body found in septic tank at Pallara in Brisbane's south
node.description: Police say the body was found in a septic tank in the yard of the home, set on a large block in Pallara.
node.content: ["A body has been found in a septic tank\u00a0in Pallara in Brisbane's south.", "Three police cars were seen late on Sunday afternoon outside the two-storey brick home, set on a large block on Brookbent Road.", "Police have not confirmed if the death is suspicious."]
